* Genus &quot;Psephotus&quot;
** Red-rumped parrot, &quot;Psephotus haematonotus&quot;
* Genus &quot;Psephotellus&quot;
** Mulga parrot, &quot;Psephotellus varius&quot;
** Golden-shouldered parrot, &quot;Psephotellus chrysopterygius&quot;
